response.overview: Meditations on friendships, comings and goings, and the joyful grief of growing up, the film serves a travel guide to the storytelling of the band’s first project. Bursting with color and humor and heart, Meet Me After Practice follows a relationship as it ignites, gleams, and then…
response.tagline: How do you keep saying hello after so many goodbyes?
response.title: Meet Me After Practice
